title: ChesterField Watchface
summary: Luxury and Elegant Chesterfield pink for Moto 360 / LG G Watch R and others...
description: Get the London 2015 Look ! Black chesterfield background, minimalistic modern graphics, pink flashy hands.. it is the Watch Face you are looking for. It is a unique watchface.I sincerely hope you'll like this android wear face, for both round and square smartwatches (moto 360, ASUS or others). As simple as possible, get a new look, for men and women !This watch face is compatible with  Moto 360 / LG G Watch / LG G Watch R / Asus Zenwatch and others...
descriptionHTML:
Get the London 2015 Look ! Black chesterfield background, minimalistic modern graphics, pink flashy hands.. it is the Watch Face you are looking for. It is a unique watchface.


I sincerely hope you'll like this android wear face, for both round and square smartwatches (moto 360, ASUS or others). As simple as possible, get a new look, for men and women !

This watch face is compatible with Moto 360 / LG G Watch / LG G Watch R / Asus Zenwatch and others...
